{
  "id": "210782bb84284368921892bffa2605b0",
  "title": "Bitmap2Material 3 Pro",
  "description": "The ultimate image to material generator, now right inside Unreal Engine 4.",
  "longDescription": "Video Preview: <a href=\"http://youtu.be/MLM7TSiqzNk\">http://youtu.be/MLM7TSiqzNk</a>\nVideo tutorial: <a href=\"http://youtu.be/9W5gHlGq6J0\">http://youtu.be/9W5gHlGq6J0</a>\n\nBitmap2Material is an incredibly powerful tool that helps you generate full, seamlessly tiling materials from any bitmap image, right within UE4. This includes PBR channels such as base color (or albedo), metallic, roughness but also normal, height, specular, curvature, AO etc., based on the most accurate conversion algorithm out there. \n\nADJUST HIGHLIGHTS AND SHADOWS: \nThis allows you to create the base color (or albedo) for PBR and can be done in just a few clicks. \n\nREMOVE SEAMS: \nBitmap2Material provides the ability to make any material tile. You do not need to care anymore about making your photography tile, B2M takes care of it for you. \n\nGENERATE THE METALLIC MAP: \nEasily obtain a metallic map from the image using simple tools, or an input mask. This feature is essential when working in PBR. \n\nFULL CONTROL OVER MICROSURFACE: \nControl and adjust the finest details of your material thanks to the comprehensive set of parameters exposed by B2M. This includes adjusting the generated roughness map, for PBR. \n\nSHAPE RECOGNITION: \nBitmap2Material is the only map extractor which can keep the original shapes of your picture among all your maps. \n\nAN INFINITY OF VARIATIONS: \nB2M offers the unique ability to randomize your material and produce infinite variations with a single click!",
  "technicalDetails": "Intended Platforms: All\n\nTo use it within UE4, you'll just need to grab the free <a href=\"hhttps://www.allegorithmic.com/substance-ue4\">Substance Plugin</a>",
